Interface GeoRssChannelData

All Known Subinterfaces:
FeedChannel, GeoRssChannel
All Known Implementing Classes:
FeedChannelImpl, GeoRssChannelDataImpl, GeoRssChannelImpl
public interface GeoRssChannelData
Interface for GeoRSS channel data containing geographic information.
